Greetings from Los Angeles, and welcome back to In the Room. In
tonight=E2=80=99s email, news and notes on Shari Redstone=E2=80=99s final m=
oves at Paramount and her eye-popping plan to settle Trump=E2=80=99s basele=
ss lawsuit against 60 Minutes. Is this a blatant play to close the $8 billi=
on Skydance deal with a Trump-aligned deal partner, even if it means sacrif=
icing press freedom and pissing off the CBS News staff? Yes, obviously. But=
 hey, these days, everyone=E2=80=99s doing it!

