* =F0=9F=8D=B8The Grill Room: On today=E2=80=99s edition of the podcast, MS=
NBC host Chris Hayes joined me to discuss how social media and smartphones =
hijacked our brains, how attention became the single most powerful currency=
 in the political economy, and why Donald Trump is singularly effective at =
